A.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-0f250c2 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"0f250c2\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-fd1b17b\" data-id=\"fd1b17b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d2c55ee elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d2c55ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInDown&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">FAMILLE CRAMER<\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b14f408 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b14f408\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Trois si\u00e8cles d'Histoire<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3f4790c0 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3f4790c0\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-custom\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-7f0c4cf9\" data-id=\"7f0c4cf9\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-537e5d7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"537e5d7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Originaire de la principaut\u00e9 du Schleswig-Holstein, puis \u00e9tablie \u00e0 Strasbourg, la famille Cramer s&#8217;installe \u00e0 Gen\u00e8ve au d\u00e9but du 18\u00e8me si\u00e8cle.<\/p><p>Les deux licornes des armoiries Cramer verront na\u00eetre des personnalit\u00e9s illustres, notamment un Premier Syndique de la R\u00e9publique de Gen\u00e8ve, des imprimeurs comptant parmi les plus c\u00e9l\u00e8bres d&#8217;Europe, des scientifiques et des banquiers.<\/p><p>Parmi eux, on remarque le math\u00e9maticien Gabriel Cramer, dont les travaux de recherche sont une contribution majeure \u00e0 la th\u00e9orie \u00e9conomique moderne.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-4e8618a9\" data-id=\"4e8618a9\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-17a0d65b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"17a0d65b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.15.0 - 20-08-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.el