 data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">un savoir-faire entrepreneurial<\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bbe758d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"bbe758d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Norinvest Holding SA<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-fbfe867 elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"fbfe867\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-34fcfd6 elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"34fcfd6\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInLeft&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dd72622 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"dd72622\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Les origines du groupe Norinvest<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8cf45cc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8cf45cc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Les origine du groupe Norinvest remontent \u00e0 1871 et sont de type industriel dans le secteur de la construction.<\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-a577b41 ); background-color: var( --e-global-color-480a82a );\">En 1944 appara\u00eet la raison sociale NORBA et avec elle l\u2019activit\u00e9 dans le secteur immobilier.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p>Suite \u00e0 la cession des activit\u00e9s industrielles, Norinvest Holding SA est inscrite au registre du commerce \u00e0 Gen\u00e8ve en 1984.<\/p><p>Le groupe Norinvest \u00e9volue alors rapidement vers le secteur financier, comme g\u00e9rant de fortune d\u2019abord et ensuite en tant que n\u00e9gociant en valeurs mobili\u00e8res (LBVM).<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-be0c97d elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"be0c97d\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;gradient&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInRight&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-feeda79 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"feeda79\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Banque Cramer &amp; Cie SA<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3b7e52f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3b7e52f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>En 2002, la rencontre entre Norinvest et Messieurs Cramer &amp; Cie donne naissance \u00e0 la Maison qui porte aujourd\u2019hui le nom de Banque Cramer &amp; Cie SA.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Des op\u00e9rations successives et la cotation \u00e0 la SIX de Norinvest Holding SA en 2008 renforcent les moyens financiers du groupe.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Au cours des dix derni\u00e8res ann\u00e9es, Banque Cramer &amp; Cie a acquis trois petites banques et un g\u00e9rant de fortune ind\u00e9pendant.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-189236c elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"189236c\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-3229908\" data-id=\"3229908\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ccd803c elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ccd803c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInDown&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">notre histoire r\u00e9cente<\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e3101c3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e3101c3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title element